name: Graduate School | University of Southern California
body: ### Welcome to Graduate School, University of Southern California. The USC Graduate School mission is to promote an outstanding educational experience for USC graduate students, to celebrate graduate student achievements, and to provide leadership in the establishment and communication of policies, standards and processes related to graduate education at USC. ### Contact US Please contact gradschool.it@usc.edu for any issues.
